\id COL Meitei: Roman Script 1st Translation
\h Colossians
\toc1 COLOSSAE-GI Misingda I-ba Paul-gi Chithi
\toc2 Colossae
\toc3 Col
\mt1 COLOSSAE-GI
\mt2 Misingda I-ba Paul-gi Chithi
\imt1 Wahoudok
\ip Colossae-da leiba misingda i-ba chithi asi pakhonchatpa Paul-na i-bani (1:1). Chithi asi Christtana poklaba matung chahi 60 muk aduwaida ikhibani. Masi Paul-na keisumsangda leiringeida i-bani, madu mahakna Rome-gi keisumsangda leiringei oiramba yai. Colossians asisu Ephesians amadi Philemon hairiba chithising asiga loinana keisumsanggi chithising haina khangnei, maramdi chithising asi Paul-na keisumsangda leiringeida ikhiba ngaktani. Colossians asi Colossae-da leiba singlupta i-bani. 2:1 da ibagumna Colossae-gi singlup asi mahakna houdokpa natte adubu mahakna madugi thoudang kharadi pugadabani haina mangonda phaoramba yai. Epaphras-ti Colossae-dagi oibanina singlup asi mahakna houdoklamba yai.
\ip Aranba tambiba khara Colossae singlupta changlakpa aduda Paul-da nungaitaba poklammi. Chithi asida masigi maramda ningthijana iri. Mapham aduda Christian oiraba Jihudi kanglup khara leiramba yai, makhoina atei Christian-singbu namduna Ariba Walepnabadagi louba haibadi Jihudigi wayel yathang maru oina un-kakpa asi innaba hotnaramba yai. Christian-singbu Tengban Mapuna yanabagidamak Christta nattana karibusu nattraga kanabusu mathou tade (1:15-20) amadi mioibagi wakhallonda yumpham oiba tambibasing adu kanadaba ngaktani (2:8) haina Paul-na thoidok hendokna iri.
\iot Yaopham Takpa
\io1 1. Paul-na chithi asi Colossae-gi singluppu khurumjaraga houdok-i \ior (1:1-2)\ior*
\io1 2. Thoidok hendokna Colossae-da thokliba aranba tambiba adugi maiyokta paokhum piba oina Christta-gi matik magun-gi maramda mahakna iri \ior (1:3–3:4)\ior*
\io1 3. Paul-gi atei chithisingda oibagumna, chithi asigi saruk tangkhaimukti Christian-singna karamna hinggadage haibagi chap chaba akaknaba tambibasing piri \ior (3:5–4:6)\ior*
\io1 4. Paul-na chithi asi khurumjaba amadi atei singlupsingda chithi asi khon thokna pathoknaba paotak piraga loisilli. \ior (4:7-18)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Tengban Mapugi aningbagi matung-inna Christta Jisugi pakhonchatpa oiraba Paul amasung eikhoigi ichin-inao Timothy-na,
\p 
\v 2 Colossae-da leiba Tengban Mapugi asengba mising amadi Christtada thajaba yaba ichin inaosingda:
\p Eikhoigi Ipa Ibungo Tengban Mapudagi\f + \fr 1:2 \ft amadi Mapu Ibungo Jisu Christtagi\f* thoujal amasung ingthaba nakhoida leiba oirasanu.
\s1 Thagatchaba amadi haijaba
\p 
\v 3 Eikhoina nakhoigidamak haijaba matamda eikhoigi Mapu Ibungo Jisu Christtagi Mapa, Tengban Mapubu eikhoina matam pumbada thagatchei,
\v 4 maramdi nakhoina Christta Jisubu thajaba aduga Tengban Mapugi mi pumnamakpu nakhoina nungsiba adu eikhoina tare.
\v 5 Achumba paojel haibadi Aphaba Paona nakhoigi naphamda ahanba lakpa matamda, maduna asa pibagi maramda nakhoina tare. Maram aduna nakhoigi thajaba amasung nungsiba adu nakhoina asa touba aduda yumpham oibani, asa adudi swargada nakhoigidamak cheksinna thamkhrabani.
\v 6 Aphaba Pao aduna yaipha thoujalsing makha tana purakli aduga taibangpan-gi mapham pumnamakta sandokli, madu nakhoina ihan hanna Tengban Mapugi thoujalgi maramda takhiba amasung madu sengna khangkhiba numitta nakhoida thokkhiba adugumna thoklibani.
\v 7 Eikhoigi\f + \fr 1:7 \ft ariba lairik kharadadi “nakhoigi” hai\f* ihut sinduna Christtagi thajaba yaba thougal touba aduga eikhoiga punna minai oiminnaba achanba Epaphras-tagi Tengban Mapugi thoujal adu tamle.
\v 8 Thawaina nakhoida pibiba nungsiba adugi maramda mahakna eikhoida tamle.
\p 
\v 9 Maram asigidamak eikhoina nakhoigi pao taba numittagi houna nakhoigidamak haijaba toktri. Ibungo mahakki Thawaina pibiba lousing amasung wakhal pumnamak adugi mapanna Tengban Mapuna nakhoibu mahakki aningbabu khanghanbinaba eikhoina haijaba leptri.
\v 10 Madu oirabadi nakhoina Mapu Ibungona pamba punsi mahing adu hingba ngamgani aduga Ibungobu pelhanba thabaksing tougani. Nakhoigi punsina makhal kayagi aphaba thabaksing puthokkani amadi Tengban Mapubu khangbada henna khumang chaosinba oigani.
\v 11 Ibungo mahakki matik mangalgi panggal pumnamakka loinana nakhoibu kalhanbiduna nakhoida akhaangkanba amadi kuina khaangbiba oihanbigani,
\v 12 Aduna mangalgi leibak aduda asengbasinggi phangpham thokpa aduda nakhoibu saruk phangbada matik chaba oihanbiba Ipa aduda harao haraona thagatchou.
\v 13 Ibungo mahakna eikhoibu amambagi panggaldagi kanbiduna mahakki nungsiraba Machanupagi leibak aduda pusinbire,
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Eph 1:7\x*Machanupa aduna eikhoibu ningtamhanbire, madudi, eikhoigi papsingbu kokpire.
\s1 Christtadi khuwaidagi henthoibani
\p 
\v 15 Christtadi uba ngamdaba Tengban Mapugi saktamni, semkhraba pot pumnamaktagi hanna pokpa aduni.
\v 16 Ibungo mahakki mapanna pot khudingmak, haibadi, swargada amadi malemda leiba, uba ngamba amadi uba ngamdabasing, phambalsing, panggalsing, wayel mapusing amasung matik leibasing; pot pumnamak Ibungo mahakki mapanna amasung mahakkidamak sembikhibani.
\v 17 Ibungodi pot pumnamaktagi hanna leiramlabani, aduga Ibungoda punsinduna pot pumnamak mapham chana lei.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Eph 1:22,23\x*Ibungodi mahakki hakchang oiriba singlupki makokni; Ibungo mahakna pumnamakta ihen henba oinaba mahakti ahouba amadi asibasinggi maraktagi hinggatpa ahanba pokpa aduni.
\v 19 Maramdi Ibungo mangonda Tengban Mapugi mapung phaba pumnamak leiba haibasi Tengban Mapugi apenbani.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Eph 2:16\x*Aduga cross-ta tabikhiba mahakki ee adugi mapanna ingthaba puraktuna malemda leiba nattraga swargada leiba oirabasu pot pumnamak Ibungo mahakki mapanna Tengban Mapuda taisinnabire.
\p 
\v 21 Matam amadadi nakhoina phattaba thabaksing toukhiba amadi phattaba wakhal khankhibagi maramna nakhoisu Tengban Mapudagi lapna leirammi amadi Ibungo mahakki yeknaba oirammi.
\v 22 Houjikti mahakki Machanupagi hakchang oina sibiba adugi mapanna Tengban Mapuna nakhoibu taisinnabire, madu nakhoibu asengba, amakpa leitaba amadi landaba ama oina nakhoibu mahakki manakta pusinbinabani.
\v 23 Aduna nakhoina thajabada tattana leiduna, chetna leppu amadi Aphaba Pao adu tabagi phangba asa adudagi lengba touganu. Nakhoina takhraba Aphaba Pao adu atiyagi makhada leiba khutsem pumnamakta sandokkhrabani, amasung Paul eidi madugi thougal touba oijare.
\s1 Paul-na touba Singlupki thougal
\p 
\v 24 Nakhoigi maramgidamak awaba khaangba asida eina haraojei, maramdi mahakki hakchang oiriba singlupkidamak Christtana awa khaangbagi wat-houriba adu eigi hakchanggi mapanna eina mapung phahalli.
\v 25 Tengban Mapuna eibu singlupki thougal touba oihanbire, Ibungo mahakna nakhoigi phanabagidamak eingonda thoudang asi tounaba pibibani. Thoudang adudi mahakki paojelbu mapung phana laothokpa aduni,
\v 26 athuppa adu houkhraba chahi kaya kaya amadi mirol kaya kaya lottuna thamlakpani adubu houjikti Mapu Ibungogi misinggi maphamda phongdokpire.
\v 27 Makhoi aduda Jihudi nattaba phurupsingda athuppa adugi mamal leiraba matik mangal khanghannaba Tengban Mapuna leple, madudi asagi matik mangal oiriba nakhoida leiriba Christta aduni.
\v 28 Eikhoina mi khudingbu Christtada katchanaba, lousing pumnamakka loinana laothokliba, warak watemliba amadi tambiriba asi Ibungo mahak asini.
\v 29 Madu tounabagidamak eigi nungda thabak touriba Christtagi panggal adu sijinnaduna eihakna kanna hotnaduna thabak su-nommi.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Nakhoigidamak amadi Laodicea-da leibasing amasung eihakpu hakthengnana unadriba makhoisinggidamak eihakna kaya wana thabak subano haibadu eina nakhoibu khanghanning-i.
\v 2 Eigi pandamdi makhoigi thamoida pukning thougatpa amadi nungsibada amata oina punsinba maduna mapung phana khangbagi athanba lan adu leiduna makhoina Tengban Mapugi athuppa haibadi Christtabu khangnanabani,
\v 3 Ibungoda lousing amadi khangbagi lan pumnamak lottuna lei.
\p 
\v 4 Kanagumba amatana phajaba manba semjin-sajinba waheising sijinnaduna nakhoibu namthak touhandanaba eina masi haibani.
\v 5 Hakchangna nakhoigi nanakta leitrabasu thawainadi nakhoigi narakta lei aduga nakhoigi phajaba lichat-sajat amasung Christtada nakhoigi thajaba chetna leiba adu ubada eina haraojei.
\s1 Christtada mapung phaba punsi
\p 
\v 6 Adunadi nakhoina Christta Jisubu Mapu Ibungoni haina lousinjaraba maramna nahakki punsi mangonda hing-u,
\v 7 Ibungo mangonda mara taduna sagatlaga, nakhoibu tambikhibagumna thajaba adu kankhat-hallu, amasung thagatchabada mapan naihan-ganu.
\p 
\v 8 Christtadagi nattaba, mioibagi kanadaba minamba lousing haibadi houkhiba miroldagi thangtharakpa tambibasing amasung taibang malem asida palliba thawaising adudagi oiba aduna nakhoi kana amatabu khudum chankhidanaba cheksillu.
\v 9 Maramdi Christtada Tengbang Mapugi oiba mapungphaba khudingmak adu lei,
\v 10 Christtada nakhoibu mapung phahanbire. Ibungo mahakti panggal pumnamakki amadi matik leiba pumnamakki makokni.
\p 
\v 11 Ibungo mangonda nakhoisu un kakle madu mioibagi khutna kakpa natte. Christtana nakhoibu un kakpiba matamda nakhoigi nathakta panba papki hakchang adu louthokpire,
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Rom 6:4\x*baptize toubada Ibungoga loinana nakhoibu leirol chanminnare, aduga mahakpu asibasinggi maraktagi hinggat-hanbiba Tengban Mapugi thabak touriba panggalda nakhoina thajabagi mapanna nakhoibu mahakka loinana hinggat-hanbire.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Eph 2:1-5\x*Nakhoigi ayol aransing amasung hakchangda un kaktaba oibagi maramna nakhoi sirambani, adubu Christtaga loinana nakhoibu\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Ariba lairik kharada “Eikhoi” haiba yao-i\f* Tengban Mapuna hinghanbire. Ibungona eikhoigi ayol aran pumnamak ngakpire;
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Eph 2:15\x*eikhoigi maiyokta leiduna eikhoibu lalhanba wayel yathanggi oiba laman tonduna leiramba adu Ibungo mahakna muthatpire; cross-ta yotpi thaduna Ibungona louthokpikhre.
\v 15 Thawaigi oiba mapusinggi panggalsing amasung matik leibasing adugi panggal louthoktuna mahakna makhoibu cross-ki mapanna maithiba piduna makhoibu iphong phongna utpikhi.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Rom 14:1-6\x*Maram aduna chaba thakpagi maramda, asengba numitsing pangthopagi maramda, nattraga thasigi nattraga potthaba numit ngakpagi maramda oirabasu kana amatana nakhoibu wayelhan-ganu.
\v 17 Masising asidi tungda oiragadabasing adugi mamini, adubu asengba adudi Christtani.
\v 18 Aranba nolukpa amadi swargadutsingbu khurumbada nungaijaba makhoina nakhoibu matik chahandaba oihan-ganu. Asigumba mi asinasu makhoina ukhiba adugi matangda yamna kupna changsilli; hakchanggi oiba pukningna arembada chaothok-i.
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Eph 4:16\x*Makhoidi makok oiriba Christtada pairamba adu tokle. Ibungo mangonda hakchang apumba asi singli naori amasung sadong masingsinggi mari manao pumnamak punsinduna yokkhatli, amasung Tengban Mapugi apamba matung inna hakchang apumba adu chaokhatpani.
\s1 Christtaga siminnaba amasung hingminnaba
\p 
\v 20 Nakhoidi Christtaga loinana siminnare aduga taibangpan asigi palliba thawaising adudagi ning tamhalle. Adu oirabadi karigi nakhoina taibangpanbagi oibagumna hinglibano? Nakhoina chatna pathapsing haibadi
\v 21 “Masi paiganu,” “Madu tangganu,” “Madu sokkanu” hairiba asigumbasing asi illibano?
\v 22 Hairiba pumnamaksing asidi ngaakna ngaakna mangkhigani; makhoising asi icham chamba mioibagi yathang amasung tambibada yumpham oi.
\v 23 Asigumba pathapsing haibadi namduna swargadutsing khurumgadabani haiba, aranba matougi nolukpa amadi hakchangbu laaknaba hairibasing asi lousingda yumpham oibadi malli adubu hakchanggi apamba adu laksinnabagidamaktadi kari amata kanaba leite.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Isei 110:1\x*Nakhoina Christtaga loinana hinggatminnarabanina, Tengban Mapugi yetthangbada Christtana phamliba mathaklomda leiba potsing aduda nakhoigi pukning thammu.
\v 2 Mathaklomda leiba potsing aduda nakhoigi pukning thammu, taibangpan-gi potta thamganu.
\v 3 Maramdi nakhoi sire, nakhoigi thawai adu Christtaga Tengban Mapuda lotminnari.
\v 4 Nakhoigi thawai oiriba Christtabu phongdokpiba matamda nakhoibusu Ibungo mahakka loinana matik mangalda phongdokpigani.
\s1 Ariba amasung anouba punsi
\p 
\v 5 Aduna nakhoida leiba taibangpan-gi oiba mahousa haibadi nupa nupi lannaba, akamba lichat, hakchanggi apamba, phattaba pamba, karaamba (karaamba haibasi lai murti latpa mawong amani), asising asi sihallu.
\v 6 Maramsing asigidamak Ibungona haiba indaba makhoising\f + \fr 3:6 \ft Ariba lairik kharada “Ibungona haiba indaba makhoising” haiba asi yaode\f* adugi mathakta Tengban Mapugi asaoba lakli.
\v 7 Matam amada apambasing asina nakhoigi nathakta pallingeida nakhoisu apambasing asigi matung inna hinglammi.
\p 
\v 8 Adubu houjikti asaoba, meihouna saoba, yengthiba wakhal, migi mangnaba ngangba amasung akaamba wa ngangba hairiba asising asi nakhoigi chindagi louthokkadabani.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Eph 4:22\x*Amaga amaga minamba ngangnaganu, maramdi nakhoigi ariba mi adu magi thabaksingga loinana louthokkhiduna,
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Eph 4:24; Meihou 1:26\x*aduga anouba mi adu setlu. Anouba oiriba adudi madu sembiba Tengban Mapuna mahakki mitamda leppa leitana nouhanbi, maduna Ibungo mahakpu mapung phana khangbada nahakpu pubiraknabani.
\v 11 Masida Jihudi nattaba phurupsing nattraga Jihudi, un kakpa nattraga kaktaba, atoppa phurup machasing, chaokhattriba mising, minai nattraga ningtamlaba mising haiba leite, adubu Christtadi pumnamak oi, amasung pumnamakta lei.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12,13 \xt Eph 4:2\x*Maram aduna Tengban Mapugi khanggatlaba, asengba amasung achanba misinggumna nungsi heiba, thoujal heiba, nollukpa, pukning tappa, akhang kanba asising asi nakhoina phi setpagum setlu.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Eph 4:32\x*Amaga amaga khaangnaduna nakhoina kanagumbagi mathakta nungainadaba leirabasu amaga amaga koknou; Mapu Ibungona nakhoibu kokpiba adugumna nakhoinasu amaga amaga koknou.
\v 14 Pumnamaksing asigi mathakta pot pumnamakpu amata oina mapungphana punsilliba nungsibabu setchillu.
\v 15 Christtana pibiba ingthaba aduna nakhoina warepsing leppada nakhoibu chingbigani; maramdi hakchang amata oina leinanaba Tengban Mapuna nakhoibu koubiba asi ingthaba asigini. Toubimal khangba oiyu.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16,17 \xt Eph 5:19,20\x*Christtagi wa adu nakhoigi nungda marangkaina leihallu; lousing pumnamakka loinana amana amabu tambinou amasung waraknou, thagat isei, singlup isei amadi Thawaigi oiba iseising sak-u; nakhoigi thamoida thagatpaga loinana Tengban Mapuda isei sak-u.
\v 17 Nakhoina thabak touba oirabasu wa ngangba oirabasu Ibungo mahakki mapanna Mapa Ibungo Tengban Mapubu thagattuna Mapu Ibungo Jisugi mingda pumnamak tou.
\s1 Christian imung manungda takpi tambiba
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Eph 5:22; 1 Pet 3:1\x*Yumpallabi nupisa, napuroibagi makha pollu, masi Christian ama oina nakhoina toupham thokpani.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Eph 5:25; 1 Pet 3:7\x*Mapuroibasa, nakhoigi nupisingbu nungsiyu, makhoida minungsi chendana loinaba touganu.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Eph 6:1\x*Angangsa, maram pumnamakta nakhoigi nama napana haiba illu, maramdi maduna Mapu Ibungogi apenbani.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Eph 6:4\x*Mapa oibasa,\f + \fr 3:21 \ft Mama mapa\f* nakhoigi nachasingbu saohan-ganu nattrabadi makhoi pukning hanthakhigani.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22-25 \xt Eph 6:5-8\x*Minaisa, maram pumnamakta nakhoina taibangpan-gi mapusinggi haiba illu, makhoigi chanbiba phangnaba makhoina uringeikhaktada touba nattaduna, thamoi sengna Tengban Mapubu kijabagi makhoina udaba matamdasu tou.
\v 23 Nakhoina touba khudingmakta mioibagi thougal toubagumna nattaduna Mapu Ibungobu thougal toubagumna thawai yaona tou.
\v 24 Phangpham thokpa adu mana oina nakhoina Mapu Ibungodagi phangjagani haiba nakhoina khang-i. Nakhoina thougal touriba adu Mapu Ibungo Christtani.
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Aniwa 10:17; Eph 6:9\x*Aranba touba makhoi pumnamakna makhoina touba aranba adugi atouman phangjagani, maramdi Tengban Mapudi mi pumnamakpu chap manaba wayelna wayelli.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Eph 6:9\x*Mapusa, nakhoigisu swargada Mapu ama lei haiba khangduna nakhoigi nanaisingbu phajana amadi chumna loinabiyu.
\s1 Takpi tambiba
\p 
\v 2 Tatpa leitana haijou, nakhoina thagatpaga loinana haijabada mit-na sing-u.
\v 3 Christtagi athuppa Ibungo mahakki paojel adu sandoknaba Tengban Mapuna eikhoida khudongchaba pibinaba eikhoigidamaksu haijabiyu. Masigi maramgidamak eihak houjik keisumsangda leiribani.
\v 4 Eina haidokpham thokpagumna mayek sengna eina haidokchanaba haijabiyu.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Eph 5:16\x*Thajadabasinggi maphamda thabak ama toubada hei sing-u, nakhoida leiba khudongchaba khudingmak kananaba ningthijana sijinnou.
\v 6 Nakhoigi wangang sangang adu matam pumnamakta nungaiba amadi taningba oihallu adu oirabadi mi khudingda karamna khumgadage haiba nakhoina khanggani.
\s1 Aroiba khurumjaba
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Pakhon 20:4; 2 Tim 4:12\x*\x - \xo 4:7,8 \xt Eph 6:21,22\x* Eikhoigi nungsijaraba ichin-inao, thajaba yaba thougal touba amadi Mapu Ibungogi thougalda eikhoiga thougalnai oiminnariba Tychicus-na eigi maram pumnamak nakhoida haibigani.
\v 8 Eina mahakpu nakhoigi naphamda thakhibagi maramdi mahakna eikhoi karamna leiri haiba nakhoida tamlaga nakhoibu harao-nungngaihannabani.
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt Phile 10-12\x*Nakhoigi mi ama oiriba aduga eikhoigi nungsijaraba amadi thajaba yaba ichil inao Onesimus-su mahakka loina chatminnakhibani. Mapham asida thokpa khudingmak makhoina nakhoida tambigani.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Pakhon 19:29; 27:2; Phile 24; Pakhon 12:12,25; 13:13; 15:37-39\x*Eiga phadok taminnariba Aristarchus-na nakhoibu khurumjari. Barnabas-ki machin manao thokpa Mark-nasu nakhoibu khurumjari (Mahakna nakhoida lakpa matamda mahakpu lousinbinaba nakhoida hannana khanghankhraba aduni.)
\v 11 Justus hainasu kouba Joshua-na nakhoibu khurumjari, Jihudi Christian-singgi marakta makhoi ahum asitana Tengban Mapugi leibakkidamak eiga suminnari, makhoising asi eingonda achouba mateng oi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Col 1:7; Phile 23\x*Epaphras, nakhoigi mi ama oiriba aduga Christta Jisugi manai asina nakhoibu khurumjari. Nakhoina Tengban Mapugi aningba pumnamakta chetna leptuna, mapung phaba oiduna amasung soidre haiba khangba oinaba mahakna thawai yaona matam pumbada nakhoigidamak haijabi.
\v 13 Nakhoigidamak, Laodicea amasung Hierapolis-ta leibasinggidamak mahakna thabak yamna kanna nommi haiba asi ei isamakna sakhi piri.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt 2 Tim 4:11; Phile 24; 2 Tim 4:10; Phile 24\x*Eikhoigi achanba doctor Luke amasung Demas-na nakhoibu khurumjari haibirak-i.
\p 
\v 15 Laodicea-da leiba ichil inaosa, Nympha amasung mahakki yumda tinnaba singluppu eina khurumjari haina tambiyu.
\v 16 Eigi chithi asi nakhoigi narakta paba loiraga Laodicea-gi singluptasu pahanbiyu, matou adugumna Laodicea singlupki chithi adu nakhoinasu pabiyu,
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Phile 2\x*aduga Archippus-ki maphamdasu, “Mapu Ibungogi maphamdagi nahakna phangjakhiba thougal toubagi thabak adu mapung phana pangthok-u,” haina tambiyu.
\p 
\v 18 Paul eina khurumjaba asi ikhutmakna ijabani, eihakki yotling phalang asi ningsingbiyu!
\p Tengban Mapugi thoujalna nakhoiga loinabiba oirasanu.
